/*READ ME File - Interactive Form Project

The goal of this project is to use javascript to dynamically validate the user inputs of a form and make sure that all information is correct before submission. 

The key objectives include:

1. Set focus on the first text field upon page load

2. Include a text field that will be revealed when the "Other" option is selected from the "Job Role" drop down menu.

3. Customize the available options in the t-shirt selection depending on theme selection

4. Validate that at least 1 activity was selected and that they user could not select activities with conflicting time schedules

5. Add functionality to the payment method such that users could choose between the credit card, paypal and bitcoin

6. Validate user inputs and prompt error messages if input was invalid */

